title: Maidan-E-Jung
subTitle: Data Guru, a powerful man, spreads terror in his village. Later, when a villager marries his widowed daughter-in-law, he sets out to seek revenge.

title: Sangharsh
subTitle: Reet, a police officer, learns about a religious fanatic, Pandey, who abducts children. She then joins forces with a prisoner in order to punish Pandey.

title: Mere Jeevan Saathi
subTitle: Prakash, an altruistic artist turned womaniser, falls in love with Jyoti. However, situation changes when he loses his eyesight after an accident and Kamini, a socialite, tortures him.

title: Insidious: Chapter 3
subTitle: Quinn, a young girl, reaches out to a powerful psychic to help her contact her recently deceased mother. However, her plan backfires when an evil spirit makes Quinn a host and hurts her physically.

title: Mastana

subTitle: When all the family property is left to Bharat, his brother wants to kill him for the wealth. Bharat overhears his plan and plays along only to return as a dacoit to set things right.

title: Aradhana

title: Ramkali
subTitle: Inspector Sultan becomes a fugitive and bandit, driven by a quest for vengeance. Later, he crosses paths with a dancer, Ramkali, and discovers that she is also seeking retribution.

title: Aa Gale Lag Jaa
subTitle: Prem, a young man, must part from his lover Preeti even though she is pregnant. Years later, they reunite, but Preeti is about to engage another man.

title: Chacha Bhatija

title: Anari

title: Mr. Azaad

title: Aankhen

title: Haathkadi
